OL,3,CThe post-Christmas failures begin, but
OL,4,CNext defies the retail gloom
OL,6,FSix days into the new year, and two
OL,7,Fwell-known high street names are
OL,8,Falready heading for administration.
OL,10,FPrivate equity firm Modella Capital
OL,11,Fsays it is the "only option" for both
OL,12,FClaire's and The Original Factory
OL,13,FShop, which together employ 2,550
OL,14,Fpeople across almost 300 shops in the
OL,15,FUK.
