OL,3,CThe post-Christmas failures begin, but
OL,4,CNext defies the retail gloom
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Next reported an
OL,7,F"overachieving" Christmas. Aldi and
OL,8,FLidl both recorded strong festive
OL,9,Fsales, and figures from Worldpanel
OL,10,Fsuggest overall food spending rose -
OL,11,Feven if shoppers were thrifty,
OL,12,Fswitching to own-label products and
OL,13,Fdiscount chains.
