OL,3,CThe post-Christmas failures begin, but
OL,4,CNext defies the retail gloom
OL,6,FRetail sales did dip in October and
OL,7,FNovember, but the Bank of England
OL,8,Freports that bank lending to
OL,9,Fhouseholds and businesses increased,
OL,10,Fand mortgage approvals held up. People
OL,11,Fsaved more, but in a way that looks
OL,12,Fmore like prudent housekeeping than
OL,13,Fpanic.
OL,15,F"This was a cautious Christmas," says
OL,16,FCatherine Shuttleworth, who runs the
OL,17,Fdigital marketing agency Savvy. "But
OL,18,Fsome retailers still have reasons to
OL,19,Fcelebrate."
