OL,3,CThe post-Christmas failures begin, but
OL,4,CNext defies the retail gloom
OL,6,FIt's worth remembering that both
OL,7,FClaire's and The Original Factory Shop
OL,8,Fwere already troubled. Both were
OL,9,Frescued from insolvency last year, and
OL,10,Ftheir current owner has now decided it
OL,11,Fcannot revive them.
OL,13,FWe'll see what, if anything, can be
OL,14,Fsalvaged from administration.
